1
00:00:03,360 --> 00:00:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="24">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font color="#838698"><b>Guesthouse Inn Ishimochi</b></font></font></font></font>

2
00:00:25,260 --> 00:00:26,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyu,</font>

3
00:00:26,940 --> 00:00:30,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would you stop by and see Grandpa 
on your way home today?</font>

4
00:00:30,320 --> 00:00:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Sure thing.</font>

5
00:00:33,360 --> 00:00:35,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

6
00:00:37,520 --> 00:00:39,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="24">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font color="#70676a"><b>Guesthouse Inn Ishimochi</b></font></font></font></font>

7
00:00:49,110 --> 00:00:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyusho-kun! Your bag, your bag!</font>

8
00:00:56,060 --> 00:00:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

9
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:59,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#393832"><font face="Times New Roman">Thank You for Choosing Us
<font face="Arial"><b>Kinme Cleaning</b></font></font></font></font>

10
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

11
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:09,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, it's so clean now!</font>

12
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:11,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Kyu. Say thank you.</font>

13
00:01:12,890 --> 00:01:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

14
00:01:14,550 --> 00:01:20,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. Thank you very much 
for choosing Kinme Cleaning.</font>

15
00:01:48,340 --> 00:01:59,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="36"><font color="#4cb7b8">{\an7}Wash <font color="#2e1a12">It</font></font></font></font></font>

16
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:59,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="36">{\an7}<font color="#2e1a12">All Away</font></font></font></font>

17
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="13"><font color="#042c22"><font face="Times New Roman">Episode<font color="#c76580"> 11   <font color="#042c22">To Help This <font color="#3e8b8f">Little Guy <font color="#042c22">Out</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

18
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:15,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the lead character wears glasses 
and is super quiet so I thought,</font>

19
00:03:15,590 --> 00:03:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">hey, is that me?</font>

20
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's lost it.</font>

21
00:03:18,590 --> 00:03:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Kyu, am I loud?</font>

22
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today, I want to talk to you 
about inflected forms.</font>

23
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For example, the modern "omowanai" 
turns into "omowazu,"</font>

24
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"omoimashita" becomes "omoikeri," 
"omou" becomes "omofu," and "omou toki"...</font>

25
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa.</font>

26
00:03:55,660 --> 00:03:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's fast.</font>

27
00:03:57,990 --> 00:03:59,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yo, Kyu.</font>

28
00:04:00,050 --> 00:04:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really should join the track club.</font>

29
00:04:05,230 --> 00:04:09,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's already... second year... 
Probably too late.</font>

30
00:04:09,140 --> 00:04:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, it would be fine.</font>

31
00:04:11,530 --> 00:04:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, give it some thought. We don't 
have a middle-distance runner right now.</font>

32
00:04:17,180 --> 00:04:21,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but... 
I still have to help at home.</font>

33
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:24,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured you'd say something like that.</font>

34
00:04:25,470 --> 00:04:27,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I'll just have to run.</font>

35
00:04:37,170 --> 00:04:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, see ya later!</font>

36
00:04:37,950 --> 00:04:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

37
00:04:48,910 --> 00:04:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyu-kun, why are you so 
spaced out recently? Not sleeping?</font>

38
00:04:52,340 --> 00:04:55,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyu's always out of orbit somewhere.</font>

39
00:04:55,190 --> 00:04:56,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

40
00:04:58,220 --> 00:05:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you gotta get enough sleep, man.</font>

41
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah, I wonder.</font>

42
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mm-hmm.</font>

43
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:02,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm asleep five seconds 
after I hit the pillow!</font>

44
00:05:03,710 --> 00:05:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen up. It's normal to want to find 
the easiest way to solve a math equation,</font>

45
00:05:09,500 --> 00:05:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but once you realize
 there's this other method,</font>

46
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">things start to get interesting.</font>

47
00:05:15,340 --> 00:05:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, so let's see you use this 
formula to determine the value.</font>

48
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:22,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sato-san?</font>

49
00:05:26,710 --> 00:05:28,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry!</font>

50
00:05:28,660 --> 00:05:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, would you mind if we slept
 in the same room tonight?</font>

51
00:05:34,420 --> 00:05:37,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. Did I wake you?</font>

52
00:05:37,660 --> 00:05:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just now in the bath,</font>

53
00:05:41,590 --> 00:05:47,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I started wondering about what could 
have caused me to be so afraid of thunder.</font>

54
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, that's about all 
we have time for today.</font>

55
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be sure to review this at home, everyone.</font>

56
00:06:04,410 --> 00:06:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, I didn't catch a single word in math.</font>

57
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:10,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ishimochi? Wakasagi?</font>

58
00:06:10,890 --> 00:06:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

59
00:06:11,950 --> 00:06:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you boys getting enough rest? 
You're sleeping in class a lot recently.</font>

60
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, whoops.</font>

61
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, sorry.</font>

62
00:06:20,150 --> 00:06:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh boy. Try to stay awake.</font>

63
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's so clean!</font>

64
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:29,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A clean bag says a lot about a person.</font>

65
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

66
00:06:34,330 --> 00:06:36,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On the other hand...</font>

67
00:06:35,820 --> 00:06:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oops.</font>

68
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:38,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wakasagi, your bag looks like trash.</font>

69
00:06:38,750 --> 00:06:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I was actually planning 
to wash it this week.</font>

70
00:06:56,550 --> 00:06:58,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Aren't you getting off, Kyu-kun?</font>

71
00:06:58,980 --> 00:06:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

72
00:06:59,690 --> 00:07:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Sorry.</font>

73
00:07:01,420 --> 00:07:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gotta go see my grandpa.</font>

74
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:04,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotcha.</font>

75
00:07:04,450 --> 00:07:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See ya.</font>

76
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:07,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. See you tomorrow.</font>

77
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The doors of the train on track two 
are closing. Please stand clear.</i></font>

78
00:07:48,490 --> 00:07:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="12"><b><font color="#3b3f41">Suzuki
Family Grave</font></b></font></font></font>

79
00:07:48,490 --> 00:07:49,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="8"><b><font color="#3b3f41">Aoki
Family Grave</font></b></font></font></font>

80
00:07:48,490 --> 00:07:51,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="8"><b><font color="#3b3f41">Nakata
Family Grave</font></b></font></font></font>

81
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:51,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="8"><b><font color="#3b3f41">Aoki
Family Grave</font></b></font></font></font>

82
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:55,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><b><font color="#3b3f41">Ishimochi Family</font></b></font></font></font>

83
00:08:16,890 --> 00:08:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><b><font color="#9a520d">Ishimochi Family</font></b></font></font></font>

84
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:30,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I might as well go up 
to the top while I'm here.</i></font>

85
00:08:35,540 --> 00:08:37,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="22"><b><font color="#e9c00d">{\an8}Izukai Shrine</font></b></font></font></font>

86
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The climb is always a pain, though.</i></font>

87
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At least it's easier now 
than when I was a kid.</i></font>

88
00:08:54,490 --> 00:08:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, what?</font>

89
00:08:56,180 --> 00:08:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinme-san? What are you doing here?</font>

90
00:08:58,620 --> 00:09:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are <i>you</i> doing here, Kyusho-kun?</font>

91
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:06,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I did some cleaning and I thought 
I'd visit the shrine while I'm at it.</font>

92
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cleaning?</font>

93
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, my grandpa's grave is down below.</font>

94
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:14,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, so you were cleaning the grave.</font>

95
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:19,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom usually takes care of it, 
but she asked me to come today.</font>

96
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

97
00:09:21,210 --> 00:09:25,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so responsible of you 
to pay respect to your ancestors.</font>

98
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but it's no exaggeration to say</font>

99
00:09:29,010 --> 00:09:33,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't be here without 
my grandpa and family.</font>

100
00:09:36,190 --> 00:09:38,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's such a nice way to see it.</font>

101
00:09:38,850 --> 00:09:43,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyusho-kun, that's one reason 
I think I like you so much.</font>

102
00:09:47,990 --> 00:09:51,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Kinme-san, I...</font>

103
00:09:51,890 --> 00:09:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

104
00:09:52,770 --> 00:09:55,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been wondering 
about something, and...</font>

105
00:10:12,540 --> 00:10:15,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What? Kyusho-kun?</font>

106
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:58,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="22"><font color="#80c4c4">{\an7}Wash It All Away</font></font></font></font>

107
00:10:58,930 --> 00:11:03,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="22"><font color="#80c4c4">{\an7}Wash It All Away</font></font></font></font>

108
00:11:08,020 --> 00:11:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unfortunately, I am a little 
backed up at the moment,</font>

109
00:11:10,820 --> 00:11:14,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm afraid it will take 
one day longer than usual.</font>

110
00:11:14,620 --> 00:11:16,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that still all right with you?</font>

111
00:11:16,260 --> 00:11:17,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that's fine.</font>

112
00:11:17,950 --> 00:11:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much. 
As always, you can count on Kinme!</font>

113
00:11:24,030 --> 00:11:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll see you then.</font>

114
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

115
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, Kinme-oneesan!</font>

116
00:11:34,300 --> 00:11:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hello. Come on in.</font>

117
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello. Looks like you're keeping busy.</font>

118
00:11:40,470 --> 00:11:43,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}Yes, I sure am.</font>

119
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#6896c8">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

120
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="16">{\an8}<font color="#e2f2fb">Refresher</font></font></b></font></font>

121
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#e3d0b6">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

122
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="19">{\an8}<font color="#7f6c56">Busy Seasons
 for Cleaners</font></font></b></font></font>

123
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f7e9ec">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

124
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="19">{\an8}<font color="#d88595">April-June
 <font size="14">(Putting Away
Winter Clothes)</font></font></font></b></font></font>

125
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#d0e8f4">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

126
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="12">{\an8}<font color="#6c80b1">September-October 
 <font size="10">(Putting Away
Summer Clothes)</font></font></font></b></font></font>

127
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#fff3c3">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

128
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="9">{\an8}<font color="#e19f63">End & Beginning of Year
(Yearly Cleaning)</font></font></b></font></font>

129
00:11:43,470 --> 00:11:47,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}We do get a lot of business 
around this time of year.</font>

130
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ce6661">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

131
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="14">{\an6}<font color="#f9f1ef">Here Now</font></font></font>

132
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ce6661">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

133
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="14">{\an6}<font color="#f9f1ef">Here Now</font></font></font>

134
00:11:47,730 --> 00:11:52,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm sorry to bother you, then,</font>

135
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but may I still ask you 
to clean these for me?</font>

136
00:11:54,910 --> 00:11:58,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, of course! Thank you very much.</font>

137
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There.</font>

138
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:03,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you taking more pictures 
for social media?</font>

139
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:04,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

140
00:12:05,500 --> 00:12:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother, I'd like to take some more 
pictures before I go home.</font>

141
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh my.</font>

142
00:12:13,740 --> 00:12:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that all right? 
It's such a busy time for you.</font>

143
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will not get in her way one bit!</font>

144
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:22,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it's fine with me.</font>

145
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:25,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Well, thank you very much.</font>

146
00:12:25,890 --> 00:12:29,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nairo, do not cause her 
any trouble at all.</font>

147
00:12:29,900 --> 00:12:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

148
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:48,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you think we've taken 
enough of this kind of picture?</font>

149
00:12:48,300 --> 00:12:49,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, definitely not!</font>

150
00:12:50,190 --> 00:12:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need newer pictures of you working
 to keep appearing on the timeline!</font>

151
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that's how it works.</font>

152
00:12:58,420 --> 00:13:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! But videos actually get 
more attention than pictures do.</font>

153
00:13:04,830 --> 00:13:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See, like this one.</font>

154
00:13:08,180 --> 00:13:11,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The number of views is... Ten thousand?!</font>

155
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ffffff">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

156
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><font size="17"><font color="#787571">10,126 Views</font></font></font></font>

157
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ffffff">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

158
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><font size="15"><font color="#787571">Here is Kinme-san, the owner of Kinme Cleaning, treating a 
stain on a customer's garment! She works very carefully, 
applying a series of detergents to safely remove the stain.</font></font></font></font>

159
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:14,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I'm the same way,</font>

160
00:13:14,100 --> 00:13:18,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but everyone seems to be really interested 
in your stain-removing steam sprayer!</font>

161
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I would love to take another video 
of you removing stains today.</font>

162
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm. But I've already pretty much 
finished stain treatment for the day.</font>

163
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? What is that over there? 
There's a square on the floor.</font>

164
00:13:33,330 --> 00:13:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? A square?</font>

165
00:13:37,590 --> 00:13:39,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you mean that.</font>

166
00:13:39,950 --> 00:13:41,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it some kind of door?</font>

167
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, probably.</font>

168
00:13:43,610 --> 00:13:45,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean you've never opened it?</font>

169
00:13:45,470 --> 00:13:50,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I tried to open it once 
soon after I started here,</font>

170
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:53,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the handle was stuck, so I gave up.</font>

171
00:14:03,530 --> 00:14:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Mm-hmm.</font>

172
00:14:03,530 --> 00:14:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mm-hmm.</font>

173
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, wow!</font>

174
00:14:20,970 --> 00:14:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nairo-chan?</font>

175
00:14:23,010 --> 00:14:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nairo-chan?</font>

176
00:14:25,300 --> 00:14:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, um, let's open it right now!</font>

177
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We might make a great discovery! 
Let's get some torches ready!</font>

178
00:14:32,390 --> 00:14:34,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Torches?</font>

179
00:14:36,770 --> 00:14:41,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Last time, I wasn't able to open it 
by pulling on the handle.</font>

180
00:14:42,280 --> 00:14:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So maybe if I try this...</font>

181
00:14:46,030 --> 00:14:46,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

182
00:14:46,900 --> 00:14:48,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's open!</font>

183
00:14:54,540 --> 00:14:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sigh.</i></font>

184
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, so it just comes right off.</font>

185
00:15:01,300 --> 00:15:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured it was underfloor storage space.</font>

186
00:15:03,430 --> 00:15:04,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}My castle...</font>

187
00:15:04,140 --> 00:15:08,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if these belong to the owner 
of the previous cleaning shop.</font>

188
00:15:09,340 --> 00:15:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything looks very worn out and rusty.</font>

189
00:15:13,300 --> 00:15:15,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it does.</font>

190
00:15:16,620 --> 00:15:18,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What could that be?</font>

191
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find something?</font>

192
00:15:21,310 --> 00:15:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A stuffed animal?</font>

193
00:15:22,940 --> 00:15:27,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a hole torn in the bag,
 so it's grown filthy.</font>

194
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:30,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a receipt!</font>

195
00:15:31,470 --> 00:15:37,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which means this must be an item that
a customer brought in to be cleaned.</font>

196
00:15:41,710 --> 00:15:45,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like it is very moldy 
and discolored.</font>

197
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel kind of bad for it.</font>

198
00:15:47,660 --> 00:15:52,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Underfloor spaces are humid 
and have poor air circulation,</font>

199
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:55,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so they aren't really suitable 
for storing things made of fabric.</font>

200
00:15:56,820 --> 00:16:00,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So why keep a customer's 
precious stuffed animal there?</i></font>

201
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aji-san did tell me that this building 
was used for another cleaning shop</i></font>

202
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#e789b7">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

203
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="30"><font color="#feefa3">Welcome!</font></font></b></font>

204
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ededea">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font>

205
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<b><font size="25"><font color="#60c8ee">2x Points
Every Tuesday</font></font></b></font>

206
00:16:07,510 --> 00:16:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>long before I moved in.</i></font>

207
00:16:10,260 --> 00:16:13,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If that previous manager 
is responsible for this,</i></font>

208
00:16:14,710 --> 00:16:18,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>as a cleaner myself, I do not approve.</i></font>

209
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:22,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong? 
You look upset about something.</font>

210
00:16:22,610 --> 00:16:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh, nothing.</font>

211
00:16:25,900 --> 00:16:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I should try to contact the owner.</font>

212
00:16:32,710 --> 00:16:37,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm. I can't get through 
to the number on the receipt.</font>

213
00:16:38,390 --> 00:16:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There is an address, though...</i></font>

214
00:16:41,220 --> 00:16:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, so what do you plan 
to do with the stuffed animal?</font>

215
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:48,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good question.</font>

216
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:52,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#928a84">{\an7}Collection Receipt
 <font size="14">Location:
 <font size="14">Name: <font size="18">Mutsu-sama

<font size="14">Date Received: June 4 
Scheduled Pick-up Date: June 25

Please bring this receipt when you come to pick up your item.
 We cannot be held responsible for items that are not claimed within one month.

 Item: Stuffed Animal</font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

217
00:16:48,710 --> 00:16:52,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If this was meant for 
the previous shop to clean,</font>

218
00:16:52,580 --> 00:16:56,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it might seem a bit presumptuous 
for me to do something.</font>

219
00:16:57,560 --> 00:17:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then again, I can't just leave 
something so dirty in this state.</font>

220
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am going to wash it.</font>

221
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:20,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm also doing it to help this 
little guy out, after being trapped</i></font>

222
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>alone in the dark for so long.</i></font>

223
00:17:31,110 --> 00:17:32,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

224
00:17:34,030 --> 00:17:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you explain what 
you're doing right now?</font>

225
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm press-washing it.</font>

226
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:41,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stuffed animals are filled with padding,</font>

227
00:17:41,410 --> 00:17:45,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I put a small amount of mildly acidic 
commercial detergent in warm water</font>

228
00:17:45,620 --> 00:17:49,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and press it gently to wash the insides.</font>

229
00:17:49,760 --> 00:17:54,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! It's like the little guy 
is taking a bath!</font>

230
00:18:01,850 --> 00:18:06,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After press-washing, I rinse it 
two or three times the same way.</font>

231
00:18:06,860 --> 00:18:11,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It isn't always clear what plush toys 
like this are stuffed with,</font>

232
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so it is best not to soak them completely 
unless absolutely necessary.</font>

233
00:18:16,870 --> 00:18:20,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, if you aren't careful to 
dry them completely afterwards,</font>

234
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they can easily become 
a breeding ground for mold.</font>

235
00:18:32,130 --> 00:18:35,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then, and then, 
what do you do after that?</font>

236
00:18:35,660 --> 00:18:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dry it.</font>

237
00:18:39,390 --> 00:18:41,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to spin it around?</font>

238
00:18:41,470 --> 00:18:45,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you spin it too hard, the stuffing 
could get bunched up</font>

239
00:18:45,140 --> 00:18:46,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and change the shape of the toy,</font>

240
00:18:47,330 --> 00:18:51,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I keep a close eye on the time 
and temperature and just dry it partway.</font>

241
00:18:51,530 --> 00:18:55,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Didn't you say you needed 
to dry it completely?</font>

242
00:18:56,200 --> 00:19:00,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, so after this, I'll take him 
to the back yard to relax.</font>

243
00:19:01,830 --> 00:19:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

244
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:12,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a flat drying net.</font>

245
00:19:12,020 --> 00:19:15,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hang it in the shade 
until it dries and then I'm done.</font>

246
00:19:15,430 --> 00:19:18,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is going to be a popular post!</font>

