290
00:19:34,940 --> 00:19:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Where did it come from?</i></font>

291
00:19:40,950 --> 00:19:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aji-san!</font>

292
00:19:42,110 --> 00:19:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

293
00:19:44,990 --> 00:19:48,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone from the moving company 
might have stuffed it under the floor.</font>

294
00:19:48,460 --> 00:19:49,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moving company?</font>

295
00:19:49,620 --> 00:19:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When the last cleaner closed shop, 
I left everything to a moving company.</font>

296
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:59,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had them clean everything and even 
sort through all the equipment.</font>

297
00:19:59,300 --> 00:20:04,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those bums had the nerve to tell me there 
wasn't anything in the underfloor storage.</font>

298
00:20:04,870 --> 00:20:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

299
00:20:06,660 --> 00:20:12,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a mess. I should have 
checked it myself to be sure.</font>

300
00:20:12,020 --> 00:20:16,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I never bothered 
to look inside until now either.</font>

301
00:20:16,490 --> 00:20:21,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't have any idea who 
brought that stuffed animal in.</font>

302
00:20:27,390 --> 00:20:30,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's really far up the hill, isn't it?</font>

303
00:20:30,180 --> 00:20:31,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

304
00:20:31,510 --> 00:20:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can see the ocean in the distance!</font>

305
00:20:33,750 --> 00:20:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, we really can!</font>

306
00:20:36,130 --> 00:20:37,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it around here?</font>

307
00:20:37,850 --> 00:20:40,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm. It should be.</font>

308
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think they remember 
bringing the stuffed animal in?</font>

309
00:20:44,630 --> 00:20:46,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I certainly hope they do.</font>

310
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:49,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see...</font>

311
00:20:49,020 --> 00:20:50,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think this is it.</font>

312
